Drew Harris (16) Quarterback  - 2020: Did not make an appearance in 2020.

Prior to Tulane: Did not see any action in one season at Austin Peay...As a freshman
data.text:
2020: Did not make an appearance in 2020.

Prior to Tulane: Did not see any action in one season at Austin Peay...As a freshman at Dodge City CC, completed 118-of-246 passes for 1,603 yards and 13 touchdowns… his 1,169 passing yards in Kansas Jayhawk Community College Conference play led the conference… also rushed for 202 yards and three scores… threw for a season-high three touchdowns in back-to-back games… passed for a season-high 281 yards and two scores in a 22-21 victory against Coffeyville CC… named KJCCC honorable mention in 2018.

High School: Played for coach Dwayne Savage at Camden HS… named to the All-South Jersey Team… ranked a two-star prospect by 247sports.com… also competed in track.

Personal: Pursing a Master of Business Administration.
